# Large generated data. The 1M-star shards are hosted on Cloudflare Pages and
# are fully regenerable from the pipeline in phase1/hpc/. Keeping them out of
# git keeps the repo light; see phase1/README.md for how to rebuild them.
phase1/web/shards/
phase1/_dev_shards_46k/
phase0/web/shards_dev46k/

# Raw pulls, integrated trajectories, packed binaries (regenerable)
phase0/data/*.csv
phase0/data/*.bin
phase0/data/*.h5
**/*.h5
web_shards.tgz
*.tgz

# Wrangler local cache (account info, deploy state)
**/.wrangler/

# Working notes, not part of the repo
PORTFOLIO.md
PROJECT_BRIEF.md
phase1/hpc/RUN.md
phase0/data/joburl.txt

# Python / OS cruft
**/__pycache__/
*.pyc
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
